<% title("#{@event.name} Donation") %>

<article class="module width_3_quarter">
  <header><h3>Make a Donation</h3></header>
  <div class="module_content">
    <p>
      Great events like ODSKC only happen with your help!  Please use the form below to make a donation to help offset the operating costs of the competition.
    </p>
    <p>
      All persons making a donation will be entered into a drawing to win the Black Pearl UL kite.  This kite has previously been used as a demo kite, and is in excellent condition.  You can read the review of this kite on <a href="http://v2.2.kiteclique.com/level-one-kites-black-pearl-ul-review/">KiteClique.com</a>
    </p>

    <p>
     There are a maximum of <strong>40</strong> donation opportunities at this time.  Each donation is <strong><%= number_to_currency(@cost) %> USD</strong> and an individual may donate up to a maximum of $100.00.
    </p>

    <p>
      Drawing for the Black Pearl UL is expected to be held on or around <strong>June 25, 2016</strong>.
    </p>
    <%= image_tag("BlackPearlUL.jpg", :alt => "Black Pearl UL", :width => "100%") %>
  </div>
</article>
<div class="clear"><br /></div>

<article class="module width_3_quarter">
  <header><h3>Support ODSKC!</h3></header>
  <%#= render :partial => "donate_form" %>
  <p>Sorry!  All donation opportunities have been taken at this time.</p>
</article>
<div class="clear"><br /></div>
